{"tid":1955848,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一食過啪咗兩粒維多c⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-04-02T18:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T04:46:16.000Z","uid":229754,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9f62e2231758404f2df09f6dea74c188d5ed0d","tid":1955848,"uid":229754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n啱啱沖維多c飲嘅時候整濕咗另一粒維多c<br />\n於是我就掉埋第二粒落去 兩粒沖一杯飲埋<br />\n<br />\n啱啱查咗<br />\n<br />\n成年人每日維他命C攝取上限約為1000毫克，由於維他命C是酸性，如果進食過多，可能造成腸胃不適和肚瀉，本身有尿道問題更會增加患腎結石風險。<br />\n<br />\n市面上的很多例如「維多C」等水溶片，一塊已含有1000毫克維他命C，已經達到成年人每日最高攝取量。<br />\n<br />\n想問下淨係會肚屙？"},{"pid":"82f26c4c4f7428fbe9123ee73d491baa517407d0","tid":1955848,"uid":342786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:27:15.000Z","msg":"一次半次飲多兩杯水is ok<br />\n無腎病既話"},{"pid":"b8383ec8f77174440c1c8a45f61ab79e0341882a","tid":1955848,"uid":21385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"會sa~"},{"pid":"71355b1a07a5a3cc06ba5b805f14e5392c895103","tid":1955848,"uid":224213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:30:24.000Z","msg":"食返啲嘢飲多兩杯水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68ed699cc0de18c96b464270a6f19d7caefd0d2","tid":1955848,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:47:35.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？我有時食3粒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為呢幾日未必得閒 食定先"},{"pid":"ce3db068704d3dd629c23efd30e8aa199c785311","tid":1955848,"uid":229754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:57:15.000Z","msg":"Thanks咁多位巴打 啱啱飲咗大大碗湯<br />\n個心定返啲"},{"pid":"d04badb79e516965134dac96e61836b67e5873c7","tid":1955848,"uid":229754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d68ed699cc0de18c96b464270a6f19d7caefd0d2","tid":1955848,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":